Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.54,0:00:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空好藍 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.32,0:00:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的一句話使內心相繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.39,0:00:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛穿上的鞋  敞開門扉的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.10,0:00:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你重合的景色使我心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.08,0:00:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢\N加速的心跳無法壓抑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.98,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人共同感受  季節不斷更替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.49,0:01:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的瞬間\N編織著邂逅的物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.47,0:01:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對紛飛的櫻花許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.79,0:01:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（#19 幸福的時間）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.37,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都看到囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.48,0:03:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位終於進展到這裡了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.06,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳別誤會了，美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今不用隱瞞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,校園裡到處都是兩位的傳聞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.67,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的事情傳得這麼開嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.21,0:03:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁忌的愛又何妨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.28,0:03:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春早就察覺到\N朝倉學長跟音夢學姊的心意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.92,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都會站在兩位這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁忌的愛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.09,0:03:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春，妳太大聲了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.33,0:03:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心，最後愛情一定會勝利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-所以請儘管打得火熱吧\N-走吧，音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先走囉，美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長、音夢學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.65,0:04:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.55,0:04:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賴子今天也不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.06,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天走到三丁目的麵店轉角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.73,0:04:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定今天也要練習外出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.93,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕會太晚所以先做好晚餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用微波加熱就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賴子很努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.45,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人的話好像還是會害怕就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有我們兩個人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.69,0:05:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得趕快寫作業囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（在加拿大的紐芬蘭島）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.35,0:06:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（19世紀末漁民們為了增加食材）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（而開始淡水魚的養殖作業）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（後來因為野生化數量劇增）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.86,0:06:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（山貓將其拿來吃導致數量增加）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.33,0:06:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（淡水魚被吃光之後\N山貓的食物不足）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（山貓便開始吃小麋鹿）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是家家酒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（以麋鹿當食物的野狼…）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天要開風紀委員會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.95,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢才要小心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.39,0:07:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要生氣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫表哥上次沒住我家就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，等等我們順便去約會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說小櫻，哥哥今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.75,0:07:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行喔，因為你們是兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以胡思亂想喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們是兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.56,0:07:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹不可以妨礙哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們約會定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.77,0:07:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以想說蹺掉委員會\N然後跑來妨礙我們喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.51,0:08:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，原來是這個意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然還有什麼意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我在校門口等你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.96,0:08:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情愈來愈麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.87,0:08:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想藉此隱瞞那個傳聞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.17,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪你這麼做的芳乃小姐真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杉並，我沒有那個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用做無聊的解釋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟朝倉妹妹的關係眾所皆知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.08,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終於實際體會到\N跟朝倉妹妹沒有血緣關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別小看地下新聞部的情報網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.83,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不是親生妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她終究還是你的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想說得太難聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.84,0:09:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要從夢中醒過來的話\N還是早一點會比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.11,0:09:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.39,0:09:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想跟六年前完全一樣的小櫻\N回到這裡的那一天起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間就出現了變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.90,0:10:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和身為哥哥的漫長歲月相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一瞬間宛如一場夢境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.54,0:10:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至感覺如果用力擁抱\N彷彿會毀壞消失的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，居然在發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在約會的時候這樣子\N對於淑女是很不禮貌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.55,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我在想事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在想音夢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.70,0:11:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有音夢不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是去吃點東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.71,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們今天是在約會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是快樂的約會喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長，你在哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春，妳怎麼這麼慌張呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢學姊昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.27,0:11:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在人在公園馬上過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢她昏倒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，妳10秒能跑100公尺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10秒跑50公尺倒是還可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，那抱歉我要丟下妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下、等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春打電話給我時\N說得妳好像快死掉一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，其實是老毛病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.39,0:12:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎因為太突然了\N美春也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.69,0:12:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，害我白擔心一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過哥哥會飛奔過來我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，這是當然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳實在太逞強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近已經常常興奮過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用這麼認真參加委員會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會這麼興奮是因為誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.59,0:13:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.79,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天雖然有參加委員會\N但也沒有認真在聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦子裡想的全部是哥哥的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.10,0:13:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果就忽然覺得頭昏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣我就會很安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.48,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.75,0:13:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這樣沒關係對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.32,0:13:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡哥哥沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.13,0:14:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心\N不欺騙自己的內心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.14,0:14:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起妳就是我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是…就是那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是戀人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是哥哥的戀人對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以永遠喜歡哥哥對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要感覺哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.94,0:15:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想以一個女性的身份被愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.41,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.95,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.96,0:16:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣，為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.67,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.02,0:16:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.92,0:16:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻樹沙沙作響讓花瓣凋零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.42,0:16:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同在描寫我內心的不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都說過只有音夢不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我的心意完全沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼中一直都只有哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.94,0:16:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這份愛我無法讓給別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（#20 擦肩而過的心意）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.99,0:17:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒐集心的碎片  想趕快送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.63,0:17:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎快要滿溢  真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.37,0:17:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴音輕響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.97,0:17:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人漫步於樹林小道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合而為一的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.48,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興地凝視著夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.32,0:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花之雨在飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.16,0:17:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由樹梢陽光所籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.80,0:17:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在累積於胸口的哀傷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.27,0:18:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更替的季節與不變的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.51,0:18:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會演奏通往未來的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.72,0:18:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛也能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠都能在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.72,0:18:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.66,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我臉上有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺上跟平常不太一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很棒對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是島上第一台彩色電視喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.23,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是愛賴床呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.17,0:20:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒跟哥哥並肩走在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，妳怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.56,0:21:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為太吵了使他忍不住搖頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.06,0:21:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害大家大叫 「地震了」\N並且拔腿就跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就說都怪這棵樹不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把樹拔起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.54,0:21:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果他腦袋中間出現一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.01,0:21:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到因為積水變成一個池塘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.59,0:21:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.02,0:22:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會唸同一所高中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.12,0:22:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（對不起）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.90,0:22:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（因為爸爸工作的調派\N所以我要搬家了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.70,0:22:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早點跟我說呢
